{# IronLung 3 - Follow-up Email Template

   Variables available:
   - prospect.first_name
   - prospect.last_name
   - prospect.title
   - company.name
   - last_contact_date
   - attempt_count
   - sender.name
   - sender.title
#}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #333;">
    <p>Hi {{ prospect.first_name }},</p>

    <p>I wanted to follow up on my previous message. I know things get busy,
    so I wanted to make sure this didn't slip through the cracks.</p>

    <p>I'd love to show you how we're helping lenders like {{ company.name }}
    save time on their origination process.</p>

    <p>Do you have a few minutes this week?</p>

    <p>Best,<br>
    {{ sender.name }}</p>
</body>
</html>
